sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant APP as Mobile / Web app
    participant AS as AppSync
    participant DT as DeviceToken<br/>(DDB tenant#user · device#id)
    participant SNS as SNS topic
    participant PQ as push-q<br/>(filter: channels ∋ push)
    participant PU as Push λ
    participant SEC as Secrets Manager<br/>(APNs .p8 · FCM service acct)
    participant APNS as APNs (HTTP/2)
    participant FCM as FCM (HTTP v1)
    participant DLQ as push-DLQ

    Note over APP,DT: ① REGISTER on login + on every token refresh
    APP->>AS: registerDevice {platform, token, appVersion, locale}
    Note over AS: tenant#user from JWT — never from body
    AS->>DT: PutItem device row (active=true)
    Note over APP,AS: on logout → unregisterDevice(deviceId)

    Note over SNS,DLQ: ② DELIVER
    SNS->>PQ: stage=deliver · channels ∋ push
    PQ->>PU: receive
    Note over PU: resolvable type? delivery-time resolved-check → suppress if resolved
    PU->>DT: get ALL active tokens for each recipient user
    DT-->>PU: devices[] (phone · tablet · web)
    Note over PU: render push template · badge = unread_ctr · collapseKey · ttl<br/>type.contentPolicy=minimal ⇒ generic title only (PII stays in the app)
    PU->>SEC: get provider credentials (cached)
    Note over PU,FCM: send to every device in parallel — one notifId per device
    PU->>APNS: notification (ios devices)
    PU->>FCM: notification (android / web devices)
    alt success (2xx)
        APNS-->>PU: ok
        FCM-->>PU: ok
        Note over PU: audit: push_delivered{deviceCount}
    else transient 5xx / 429
        Note over PU,PQ: backoff retry → push-DLQ after maxReceive
        PQ->>DLQ: ALARM
    else permanent (Unregistered / BadDeviceToken / NOT_REGISTERED)
        APNS-->>PU: 410 Unregistered
        PU->>DT: mark token active=false (PRUNE) — do NOT retry
        Note over PU: dead device cleaned up — other devices unaffected
    end
